\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 God has a lot of Titles...and therefore attributes about WHO He is...but He has one name...\
\ls5\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 And my fear is there are some things that are lost when we just refer to God as God...when it's just Lord God like the text says and we never speak to Him as a person from a position.\
