\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 A title creates RESPECT but a name builds a RELATIONSHIP\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl2\cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9642 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 We tend to refer to God has as LORD GOD\
\ls6\ilvl2\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9642 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 And I get it...it's in the Bible...it's WHAT HE IS.\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\sa320\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl2\cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9642 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
